    "texte_orig": "Though[SP]the[SP]rumor[SP]says[SP][1432][NULL][NULL][0014]no[SP]one[SP]knows[SP]where\nthe[SP]exit[SP]is,[1432][NULL][NULL][0014][SP]there[SP]was[SP]supposedly[SP]one\nperson[SP]who[SP]did[SP]escape...",
