    "data_size": 260,
    "nom_orig": "Maya",
    "texte_orig": "Yes![SP]That's[SP]it![SP]You're[SP]not[SP]the[SP]only[SP]thing\nthat[SP]appears[SP]in[SP]a[SP]mirror.[SP]Think[SP]about[SP]when\nyou[SP]drive[SP]a[SP]car[SP]or[SP]ride[SP]your[SP]bike!",
